<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٥٨ ... سُورَةُ المُجَادِلَةِ ... آياتها ٢٢ ... مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُجَادِلُكَ}</span> ... تُرَاجِعُكَ،<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span> خَوْلَةُ بِنْتُ ثَعْلَبَةَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَوْجِهَا}</span> ... أَوْسِ بْنِ الصَّامِتِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُظَاهِرُونَ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> يَقُولُ الرَّجُلُ لِامْرَأَتِهِ:</span> أَنْتِ عَلَيَّ كَظَهْرِ أُمِّي.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِنْ أُمَّهَاتُهُمْ}</span> ... مَا أُمَّهَاتُهُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُنكَرًا}</span> ... فَظِيعًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَزُورًا}</span> ... كَذِبًا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَعُودُونَ}</span> ... يَرْجِعُونَ عَنْ قَوْلِهِمْ، وَيَعْزِمُونَ عَلَى وَطْءِ نِسَائِهِمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتَحْرِيرُ رَقَبَةٍ}</span> ... عِتْقُ رَقَبَةٍ مُؤْمِنَةٍ؛ عَبْدٍ، أَوْ أَمَةٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَتَمَاسَّا}</span> ... يَسْتَمْتِعَا بِالجِمَاعِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُحَادُّونَ}</span> ... يُشَاقُّونَ وَيُخَالِفُونَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كُبِتُوا}</span> ... خُذِلُوا، وَأُهِينُوا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَّجْوَى ثَلَاثَةٍ}</span> ... تَنَاجِي ثَلَاثَةٍ بِحَدِيثِ سِرٍّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِمَا لَمْ يُحَيِّكَ بِهِ اللَّهُ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> قَالُوا لَكَ:</span> السَّامُ عَلَيْكُمْ،<span class="c5"> أَيِ:</span> المَوْتُ لَكَ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَوْلَا}</span> ... هَلَّا.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَسْبُهُمْ}</span> ... كَافِيَتُهُمْ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَصِيرُ}</span> ... المَرْجِعُ، وَالمَآلُ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>